OL,3,CMan found guilty after filming himself
OL,4,Cplanning to carry out terrorist attack
OL,6,FThe jury at Birmingham Crown Court
OL,7,Fdeliberated for five hours and 48
OL,8,Fminutes before convicting Savage of
OL,9,Fone count of engaging in conduct in
OL,10,Fpreparation for terrorist acts in
OL,11,FMarch last year.
OL,13,FThe trial heard how Savage was
OL,14,Farrested after sending online messages
OL,15,Fto someone he did not know was an
OL,16,Fundercover officer, saying he was
OL,17,Fwaiting to see what "opportunities
OL,18,Fcome to present itself".
