OL,6,FThey also heard how Savage had taken
OL,7,Fscreenshots of the West Midlands
OL,8,FPolice headquarters, police stations
OL,9,Fin Perry Bar, as well as various
OL,10,Fmilitary locations in Birmingham.
OL,12,FSavage also told the undercover
OL,13,Fofficer "he was putting his head on a
OL,14,Fchopping block".
OL,16,FThis was the moment Savage was
OL,17,Farrested by Counter Terrorism Police
