OL,6,FOpening the case for the Crown on 14
OL,7,FJanuary, prosecutor Peter Ratliff
OL,8,Falleged that Savage had planned to
OL,9,Fcommit and film an attack.
OL,11,FHe told the court the defendant
OL,12,Fconverted to Islam at some point in
OL,13,Fthe 2010s and followed an "extreme and
OL,14,Fviolent" part of the Salafi movement
OL,15,Fof which organisations such as al
OL,16,FQaida and so-called Islamic State were
OL,17,F"particularly notorious" examples.
