OL,3,CMan found guilty after filming himself
OL,4,Cplanning to carry out terrorist attack
OL,6,FSavage claimed the mosque he filmed
OL,7,Foutside needed "flattening" and spoke
OL,8,Fabout how his alleged targets were to
OL,9,Fbe "hunted down".
OL,11,FIn early 2024 Savage broke the handle
OL,12,Foff a kitchen knife and replaced it
OL,13,Fwith cloth before changing his social
OL,14,Fmedia status to "lone wolf".
OL,16,FThe court heard how Savage went to the
OL,17,Farea around the mosque on 11 March
OL,18,F2024 and recorded three mobile phone
OL,19,Fvideos.
