OL,7,Fmade internet searches about homemade
OL,8,Ffirearms and ammunition, including
OL,9,Fpipe guns, nail guns, firing pin
OL,10,Fmechanisms and shell casings.
OL,12,FSavage was remanded in custody and he
OL,13,Fwill be sentenced in early April.
